NOTE: 1) We converted out Training data to match the provided Test data. 2) After cleaning the data for NA values and providing imputations where needed we were left with  509 from 653 of test data provided to us. 3) We used the provided test to predict the outcome and exported it to a new csv. 

NOTE: The predicted outcome has a few missing id_student that we chose to drop before predict as they had variables missing values.

We used GBM with 90:10 split and Cross validation with 10 folds
